      <ul>
        <li><strong>Company overview:</strong> A profitable HVAC, plumbing, and refrigeration home-services contractor based in <strong>Canada</strong>, with owned real estate / land included in the sale. Listed on DealStream (so8acs) 2025-01-03, renewed 2026-04-01; broker-represented (name withheld).</li>
        <li><strong>Financial highlights:</strong> Revenue range $2.76M–$2.91M USD (mid $2.83M); SDE range $291K–$363K USD (mid $327K) — ~11.5% SDE margin. Asking $1.96M USD → ~6.0x SDE. All figures converted from CAD at $0.73/USD.</li>
        <li><strong>Buy Box summary:</strong> <strong>FAIL</strong> — non-US (Canada) is a hard geographic reject; SDE below the $1M EBITDA floor; ~6.0x ask exceeds the 5.5x negotiation tolerance.</li>
